{"tid":2265422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"轟拜登文遭拒刊 普立茲得主辭職","createTime":"2020-10-31T12:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T12:17:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca5dbe421f5909d0fc44fcb7f0ba999d3867f7b5","tid":2265422,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201031/FDSFAIIUIFFZHD6K26UKXMOMOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201031%2FFDSFAIIUIFFZHD6K26UKXMOMOI%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=0872b1cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201031%2FFDSFAIIUIFFZHD6K26UKXMOMOI%2F&h=4170e01b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201031/FDSFAIIUIFFZHD6K26UKXMOMOI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n轟拜登文遭拒刊 普立茲得主辭職<br />\n<br />\n參與揭破美國「稜鏡計劃」 而獲新聞界最高榮譽普立茲獎的記者格林沃爾德 （Glenn Greenwald）前日披露，他有份創辦的新聞網站「The Intercept」，對他一篇批評民主黨總統候選人拜登的報道作出審查並拒絕刊出，他因此已辭職。網站則反指格林沃爾德自甘降低新聞標準。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：特朗普力推美國夢  搶拜登拉美裔票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s3XYthHcSRgxL-N5B_6ooqHuNgA=/1092x728/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PAUULHTCQZGURBNZC3ANFWAUYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs3XYthHcSRgxL-N5B_6ooqHuNgA%3D%2F1092x728%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPAUULHTCQZGURBNZC3ANFWAUYI.jpg&h=eba9f1a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■格林沃爾德<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾與斯諾登揭美監控計劃<br />\n<br />\n53歲的格林沃爾德前日在網誌發文，指控The Intercept編輯群「審查我本周寫的一篇文章」、表明要「刪除文中批評拜登的所有段落、否則拒絕刊登，是侵犯了我編輯自由的合約權利」。The Intercept是格林沃爾德與「叛諜」斯諾登合作揭美國監控計劃後，2014年與另兩名記者共同創立的調查報道媒體。<br />\n<br />\n格林沃爾德在文中指控主流傳媒偏袒拜登，批評眾多傳媒對《紐約郵報》。。。。。。。。。。，指他在烏克蘭有不當商業活動，透過安排與拜登接觸牟利。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：拼關鍵佛州 造勢會防疫迥異<br />\n<br />\n現居巴西的格林沃爾德並批評，The Intercept走向「充斥壓制與審查、意識形態同質化的主流傳媒的趨勢」。<br />\n<br />\n但The Intercept隨即反駁，指他們只是要求格林沃爾德在文中為指控提出證據。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國司法部官員確認，聯邦調查局（FBI）去年開始調查亨特與商業拍檔涉洗錢的指控，調查目前未結束。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/美國《紐約郵報》"},{"pid":"664a1ee6afa14cb77f90d5f66b1e550b96214838","tid":2265422,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}